Donna D'Errico https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Donna_D%27Errico 0 Donna Jeanette D'Errico (born March 30, 1968) is an American actress and model who posed for Playboy magazine as its Playmate of the Month for September 1995 and had a starring role (1996-1998) on the television series Baywatch. She is of Italian descent. She continues to act in films and on television.
